The U.S. Agriculture Department forecast Argentina's 1986/87 coarse grain crop 13.99 mln tonne v 15.44 mln tonne month. It estimate 1985/86 crop 17.06 mln tonne v 17.14 mln month. USDA forecast Argentina's 1986/87 wheat crop 9.00 mln tonne v 9.00 mln tonne month 1985/86 crop project 8.50 mln tonne v 8.50 mln month. USDA forecast Argentine 1986/87 coarse grain export 6.60 mln tonne v 7.73 mln tonne month project 1985/86 export 9.43 mln tonne v 9.58 mln month. Reuter 